{"tid":326762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老會比返你？]患癌未婚妻離世　男失手機珍貴相片　fb籲拾獲者交還","createTime":"2017-07-18T08:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T11:26:48.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae28860cf51eb7be96c28f2899cb02ff84077d94","tid":326762,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:57:40.000Z","msg":"2017-07-18 15:48<br />\n<br />\n「在一間餐廳裡，我裝作遺失銀包要她幫忙找；她找到後看見戒指好驚訝，半分鐘後眼淚湧出來&hellip;&hellip;」兩年前，文先生向患腦癌的女朋友求婚，用手機拍下這段浪漫經歷，但未幾未婚妻便不敵病魔離世。<br />\n<br />\n更不幸的是，紀錄求婚片段的電話最近遺失，珍貴回憶或永遠失去。文先生想盡辦法都無法尋回手機，唯有在網上求助，希望拾獲者交還：「好傷心沉重，但暫時未放棄，還有一線生機。」<br />\n<br />\n文先生稱，遺失電話機身黑色，有紅色機套，螢幕右上角有裂痕，而螢幕背景是電影《第一滴血》男主角Ramboo的劇照。（fb專頁「元朗人」圖片）"},{"pid":"02bb9e435cc1569e8fbf6304040ba7d7cd55092a","tid":326762,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/165802_1dcf5f36c9cc5e04d669bc5291e3711c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F165802_1dcf5f36c9cc5e04d669bc5291e3711c.jpg&h=71ec5770&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b07c4ecaa7ba89bd23811f391d68c3d93a41a33a","tid":326762,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb0ae3531aabdf07c39614399bd323d4fecc5f85","tid":326762,"uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"講到咁重要  自己又唔Backup"},{"pid":"d520d13ae8c422ef26809e997852289c4d6bfc49","tid":326762,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebd937b1c465437bb863337e80971a4e1992d5a2","tid":326762,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講到咁重要  自己又唔Backup</blockquote><br />\n咪係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點呀, 條友唔柒都柒左啦。。<br />\n你係咪見到佢出post 話就算搵返都唔Backup 呀?"},{"pid":"9b